  "title": "Class 4 Driver #66177",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Transportation and Storage Service Provider</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Class 4 Prime Mover Driver</strong></li><li>Working Location: West – Boon Lay</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Gross Up to SGD 5000 (Attendance Allowance + Trip Allowance) + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Safely transport container units to and from Singapore ports to various customer premises</li><li>Collect and return container units from container depots, ensuring a smooth handover process to and from customer sites</li><li>Adhere to all traffic and transportation laws while maintaining a record of container movements and condition</li><li>Conduct pre-trip and post-trip vehicle inspections to ensure the prime mover is well-maintained and report any issues or discrepancies</li><li>Coordinate with dispatch and management teams to ensure efficient route planning and timely deliveries</li><li>Maintain communication with the control room and customers regarding delays, unforeseen issues, or changes in delivery schedules</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. 1 year of working experience</li><li>Must have Class 4 Driving License</li><li>Preferably have experience in driving Prime Mover</li><li>Knowledge of local route and traffic regulations</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#66177 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
